Apparatus criticus

  • Text as reported by Carettoni; note that the presence of interpuncts in lines 1 and 2 is inferred from the transcription, but typographically these are not distinguished from dots marking missing characters;
  • 1: Carettoni indicates the base of a vertical stroke as visible for the second character

translation

commentary

The fragment has not yet been identified among the various fragments in the excavation stores on site. Carettoni only provides the thickness of the stone and letter-heights.
